<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to EcoLearn!</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f7f7f7; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 0;">
          <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
            <tr>
              <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a, #34d399); padding: 32px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff;">
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">Welcome to EcoLearn, <%= name %>!</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px; color: #111827;">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px;">
                  Thanks for joining the EcoLearn community! You're just one step away from accessing interactive lessons, eco challenges, and a vibrant community of learners.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px;">
                  Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:
                </p>
                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0 0 32px;">
                  <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a, #34d399); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: bold;">
                    Verify email
                  </a>
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #6b7280; margin: 0 0 24px;">
                  If you didn't create an EcoLearn account, you can safely ignore this email.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                  Happy learning,<br />
                  The EcoLearn Team
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
